  "prompt": "What is the best and most economic perfume for men in India?",
  "response": "Finding the best and most economical perfume for men in India involves considering factors like scent profile, longevity, and price. Here are a few popular and budget-friendly options:\n\n1. **Wild Stone Perfumes**: Wild Stone offers a variety of fragrances that are quite popular among men in India. They have a good range of options at affordable prices, often under \u20b91000.\n\n2. **Fogg Fragrances**: Known for their long-lasting formulas, Fogg provides a range of body sprays and perfumes that are budget-friendly. They are widely available across India.\n\n3. **Davidoff Cool Water**: Although a bit pricier than typical budget options, you can often find it on sale at around \u20b92000. This classic scent is fresh and aquatic, making it a good choice for everyday wear.\n\n4. **The Body Shop's White Musk**: Priced moderately, this perfume offers a unique musk fragrance that is both light and appealing. \n\n5. **Nautica Voyage**: Sometimes available for under \u20b92500 during sales, it provides a fresh aquatic aroma and is generally well-received.\n\n6. **Jack & Jones Fragrances**: These come at reasonable prices and offer a mix of casual and sophisticated scents.\n\nWhen selecting a perfume, it\u2019s advisable to try a few scents on your skin to see how they react with your body chemistry, as this can significantly affect the fragrance. Shopping during sales or using e-commerce platforms can also help in finding better deals on these perfumes.",
